    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
        <p>The Redstone Community Big Band is a group of like-minded, amateur musicians of all ages, that get together once a week to
           play arrangements of classic big band jazz, swing, latin and contemporary music.</p>
        <p>Originally formed in 2005 we are currently directed by Graham Russell, a professional musician with 40 over
           years experience and a love of the big band genre. Since Graham began leading the band, his skill
           and enthusiasm has helped Redstone go from strength to strength.</p>
        <p>The band performs regular public concerts throughout the year, raising money for our nominated local charities,
           as well as occasional private bookings: local shows, wedding anniversaries etc.</p>
