<div class="content-section join">
    <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Joining the band</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="section-body">
        <p>Redstone is a community big band and as such we are open to anyone, provided that you play a traditional big band
           instrument and can read music at grade level, or above. No previous jazz experience is necessary and there are no auditions.</p>
        <p>However, although we don't limit our sections to traditional big band sizes (we currently have 10 alto sax players
           for example!), we are constrained by our rehearsal space and concert logistics.</p>
        <p>If you are interested in becoming a member then send us an email.</p>
    </div>

